**Tool #2: grep_repo**


{
  "pattern": "143/157|synthesis-miss|retrieval-miss",
  "path": "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md"
}

Respuesta

```json
{
  "matches": [
    "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md:12: - Canonical scoreboard (S190 arbiter rerun, unchanged since): **143/157 facts OK (91.08%)** — 12 synthesis-miss, 2 retrieval-miss. Target ladder: 91% CLEARED; next 93% needs +4 net facts.",
    "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md:31: - SETTLED (kill): answer rewrite/addendum family — S181 (append), S183 (schema-first), S200 (sectional rewrite), S205 (claim-extractor rewrite): all NO-GO/ROLLBACK on PASS-rate or fact regressions. Do NOT reopen as \"rewrite\".",
    "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md:34: - SETTLED (kill): S216 decomposition-synthesis (question split + per-focus writers + merge): NO-GO — 4/7 synthesis gains but 3 fact regressions and cost 2.4x; merge step reintroduced monolithic-rewrite failure mode.",
    "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md:37: - OPEN: synthesis-miss family (12 facts) remains the top lever; no structural approach has yet produced stable gains without regressions. S224 unit-level binding sketch parked as PROMISING-UNVALIDATED.",
    "docs/LEVER_DIGEST.md:41: - OPEN: retrieval-miss (2 facts) — settled as not-worth-pursuing at current corpus scale (S190)."
  ]
}
```

**Tool #3: grep_repo**

action
{
  "pattern": "S224|S227|S228",
  "path": "docs/DECISIONS.md"
}

Respuesta

```json
{
  "matches": [
    "docs/DECISIONS.md:210: - S224: unit-level source binding sketched (planner assigns evidence units to obligations; per-obligation writers; deterministic assembler). PARKED as PROMISING-UNVALIDATED pending a clean diagnostic design. Key open risks recorded: planner sees question only (no answers/golds), output budget must be aggregate not per-block, assembler must not rewrite.",
    "docs/DECISIONS.md:212: - S227: Kidde external cohort attempt halted at item 1 — Fable 5 frontier reviewer hit max_tokens on first item; prereg declared no-retry, so cohort closed INCOMPLETE. External validation of S217-line remains missing. No score credit claimed.",
    "docs/DECISIONS.md:214: - S228: (this session) clause-bound synthesis diagnostic design; see evals/s228_clause_bound_synthesis_design_v1.md."
  ]
}
```

